==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: ā shān

====Proper noun====
'''[[阿]][[山]]'''
#a familiar way of calling someone who's given name ends with [[山]].

===[[Taiwanese]] [[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: a-soaⁿ

====Etymology====
A slang term originally derived from the middle character of [[唐山人]].  [[阿]] is used to describe person in the familiar sense.

====Noun====
'''[[阿]][[山]]'''
#(In Taiwan) an old-fashioned term used to describe Chinese peoples not originally from Taiwan.  This term later came to be replaced by [[外省人]].

===Related terms===
*[[大陆人]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
*[[大陸人]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
*[[唐山人]]

